    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carry Onward是一个叙述性的游戏短片，讲述了一个正在悲痛中的男人打包他的家。通过与物品互动，让自己沉浸在他的思想和情感中，感受记忆的变革力量以及从接受变化中产生的希望。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353440/extras/6b3921b3fcb00fc812916d0bdaf4a6dd.poster.avif?t=1743070839\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353440/extras/6b3921b3fcb00fc812916d0bdaf4a6dd.webm?t=1743070839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353440/extras/6b3921b3fcb00fc812916d0bdaf4a6dd.mp4?t=1743070839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与看似普通的物品互动，每一个都对托马斯和他的过去有特别的意义，并探索一个寻求安慰和目的的男人的内心思想和情感。见证即使是最小的瞬间也能对我们的生活产生深远影响，并塑造我们是谁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353440/extras/b1b2b83369be6e9b754d0351da5c1996.poster.avif?t=1743070839\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353440/extras/b1b2b83369be6e9b754d0351da5c1996.webm?t=1743070839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353440/extras/b1b2b83369be6e9b754d0351da5c1996.mp4?t=1743070839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特性：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>开始一段短暂的旅程</strong>: 由独立开发者设计的可以在一个晚上完成的一款游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>塑造结局</strong>: 你的选择将塑造托马斯的情感旅程，引导到五个可能的结果之一。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>探索人的内心世界</strong>: 在陪同他进行自我发现的旅程中，揭示托马斯的思想和情感的深度。</p></li></ul>",
